data.description: If your looking to be in the heart of Central Denver, look no further! Simply located in one of the BEST up and coming areas Denver has to offer! Close to City Park, Denver Zoo, Museum, Downtown Denver, Cherry Creek Shopping, Medical facilities and so much more!  As you arrive you will love the west facing lot giving you plenty of natural sunlight. Step inside and your greeted with beautifully refinished hardwood floors and an open floor plan which normally is non-existent in this era of construction. The kitchen has been remodeled recently and features really nice stainless steel appliances, gorgeous countertops and new white cabinets that  makes this one shine. There is a little eating nook just off the kitchen that is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee with it's sun drenched windows that wrap around the space. Need a little office area, you can always convert this space to accommodate a small desk and soak up the sun while you work. This home has some nice extras too, like the utility sink the garage, a large storage shed in the backyard with electricity already installed, pull down storage in the garage attic space as well as extra storage in the laundry room area with additional cabinets and countertop space. The huge backyard is an open slate to make it your own private oasis or add on to the property and increase your living space, the possibilities are endless. New plumbing, roof, gutters, windows, washer, dryer, hot water heater and paint are just some of the newer items to give you peace of mind. Truly move-in ready. Featuring great character and charm along with backing to million dollar plus properties, you don't want to miss out on this opportunity to live in one of the coolest neighborhoods in Denver. Easy access to highways, DIA, public transportation and so much more! Hurry and schedule a showing soon, you will not be disappointed.
